1
00:00:02,474 --> 00:00:07,474
LEARN. Cognitive-development analytics for USMC schoolhouses.

2
00:00:07,476 --> 00:00:12,476
LOGCOM use case: Learning Intelligence Dashboard. Are Marines actually learning?

3
00:00:12,478 --> 00:00:17,478
Eighteen students. Six assignments. Two hundred forum posts. One question.

4
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:23,480
Synthetic Moodle export streams in. No data movement.

5
00:00:23,488 --> 00:00:29,488
A three-stage agent scores every student against the USMC competency rubric, anchored to NAVMC 3500.18 Infantry T&R.

6
00:00:29,519 --> 00:00:37,519
A Kamiwaza-deployed model drafts the Instructors Competency Brief, cited to NAVMC 3500.18.

7
00:00:31,526 --> 00:00:38,526
Three-click drill-down: heatmap to student to remediation. Sergeants Course at SNCO Academy is distinct from the Squad Leader Course at SOI.

8
00:00:38,533 --> 00:00:44,533
Class-level competency map. Top performers. Intervention list.

9
00:00:44,537 --> 00:00:51,537
Every assessment SHA-256 chained. Privacy Act of 1974 and DoDI 1322.35 governed. SJA, IG, TECOM can replay.

10
00:00:51,543 --> 00:00:59,543
Powered by Kamiwaza. Privacy Act 1974 and DoDI 1322.35 governed. IL5 ready. Deploy in hours.
